      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It makes sense that you feel disconnected when the only presence you have is the silence itself. Please focus on being gentle with yourself right now, as your pain is valid and you do not have to solve everything immediately. Reaching out to a trusted non-emergency resource like the 988 Suicide & Crisis Lifeline can offer someone to listen to you without judgment, even if you don't think a phone call can \"fix\" anything. You are not alone in this struggle.",
